{"tid":2044201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"組織指五成失業家庭租金超綜援上限　質疑津貼水平與市場脫節","createTime":"2020-05-31T03:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:51:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ba173a13c1b6a06df1fdecba9865cd387958b2","tid":2044201,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"肺炎疫情在全球持續，政府公布四月失業率為4.2%，對比三月上升1%。綜援權利大聯盟、關注綜援低收入聯盟、香港社會工作者總工會於今年5月18日至24日展開「疫情下綜援政策支援失業人士的意向調查」，對象為正在失業或於疫情曾失業的街坊。以口頭訪問和網上問卷形式抽樣進行，共調查了131份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，超過九成受訪者居住租住單位，接近五成家庭租金開支超出綜援租金津貼上限，反映綜援租金津貼水平與市場脫節。而政府曾表示申請綜援與租金開支並無關係，但受訪家庭中，部分被「租金過高」為由被拒絕，除非他們搬往租金更低的單位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4586516/org/f770aa5b490dc6528e3b8839cd69d542.jpg/V-TBCvR63W7UPQNtI0NOTdnQVqwEjofYWczNGlnMzRo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4586516%2Forg%2Ff770aa5b490dc6528e3b8839cd69d542.jpg%2FV-TBCvR63W7UPQNtI0NOTdnQVqwEjofYWczNGlnMzRo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=57edbf8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18407bb5063375d66373371673b430ee9d2bbc15","tid":2044201,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"政府：可以搬去大灣區住"},{"pid":"7cab8d28109f738d51b24c3e49b8739cfed14604","tid":2044201,"uid":346701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以迫佢地出去工作,好事黎喎"},{"pid":"018301f5f8b548d0ec601b119c9229b6d11fae97","tid":2044201,"uid":34235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18407bb5063375d66373371673b430ee9d2bbc15","tid":2044201,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"政府：可以搬去大灣區住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"啱啦 成班新移民可以同家人團聚"},{"pid":"6878d143cf6971312e6ddeb4e4c702f77c5ca49b","tid":2044201,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"對呢種家庭黎講<br />\n攬唔攬炒無咩分別⋯<br />\n日子一樣苦"},{"pid":"5ac932967b3747ab844414aa472727d1644aa23a","tid":2044201,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cab8d28109f738d51b24c3e49b8739cfed14604","tid":2044201,"uid":346701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以迫佢地出去工作,好事黎喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"講緊自己未必搞得掂又拎唔到援助個啲<br />\n唔係班垃圾新移民，佢哋駛撚做咩"},{"pid":"afd1487b224949937df869742dd21eda4c2682c9","tid":2044201,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18407bb5063375d66373371673b430ee9d2bbc15","tid":2044201,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"政府：可以搬去大灣區住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"低端人口移除計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeeefbb277cd6ae36c11284f93688d60d01c73c","tid":2044201,"uid":301100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cab8d28109f738d51b24c3e49b8739cfed14604","tid":2044201,"uid":346701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以迫佢地出去工作,好事黎喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"真係唔做野嘅就唔洗住貴租區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}